# june

a compiler and vm for a small lisp implemented in c++

## example

    (define (fib n)
        (if (< n 2)
            1
            (+ (fib (- n 1)) (fib (- n 2)))))

a longer example found at `fib.lisp`

## prerequisites

you need bazel: https://bazel.build/install or `brew install bazel` on mac

## building

    bazel build //src:june

## usage

    ./bazel-bin/src/june <file>

